      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加，accTitle是\"Q Revenue Chart\"，accDescr写成\"Quarterly revenue comparison\"。纵轴标签我设为\"Revenue ($K)\"，横轴标签是\"Quarter\"，这样清晰吗？",
